<Base title="Affiliate Disclosure — DeveX Tools">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 32px; max-width: 740px; margin: 40px auto;">
    <h1 class="page-title">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <section style="margin: 32px 0; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;"><strong>DeveX Tools is committed to transparency.</strong> Here's how our reviews and recommendations work:</p>

      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li><strong>Zero sponsored placements.</strong> No tool can pay to appear on DeveX. Every review is independent.</li>
        <li><strong>Affiliate links.</strong> Some product links on this site are affiliate links. If you click and make a purchase, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.</li>
        <li><strong>No influence on ratings.</strong> Affiliate relationships do not affect our ratings, rankings, or editorial content. Tools are reviewed solely on merit.</li>
        <li><strong>Third-party ads.</strong> We display Google AdSense ads. These are managed by Google and are not directly sold by us.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>If you have questions, contact <a href="mailto:hello@devex-tools.net">hello@devex-tools.net</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
